snippet.title: Best VGM 872 - The Legend of Zelda - Intro (Series' 25th Anniversary)
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 200 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nH7ma8TPnE8

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

NES
The Legend of Zelda (1986)
Intro
Koji Kondo
